{"tid":762143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[豆腐渣+史上最貴鐵路] 鏗鏘集：差之毫釐","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T18:26:36.000Z","uid":41818,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b66e14fae5ef812fa9d5170967e82e826fab3b9","tid":762143,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8udriKX67Uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8udriKX67Uk&d=IuKNOLbpE%2FhetUGzojZuLZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3efc182c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8udriKX67Uk</a><br />\n<br />\n造價近千億的沙中綫，近日牽涉多宗工程醜聞，其中紅磡站擴建工程月台，更有人將鋼筋剪短。 究竟誰人剪鋼筋？多少鋼筋被剪？事件中港鐵與政府，又否做好監督角色呢？承建商、分判商、港鐵同政府，出現不同版本的說法。 被剪短的螺絲頭，只差毫釐，但有機會構成公眾安全危機。 這條香港史上最貴的鐵路，超支、延誤。連串的工程醜聞背後反映的監管問題，責任誰屬？"},{"pid":"fb3ef748879218d9d499541b43a66ed667639ede","tid":762143,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"而家件事係咪不了了之左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好似已經無曬聲氣"},{"pid":"d9626cfe7f1a56e33cb13111e6af13e1c490ba88","tid":762143,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"屎上最貴豆腐渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75f7ea90e391760376b17083eff2fe6c01d0c0f","tid":762143,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9626cfe7f1a56e33cb13111e6af13e1c490ba88","tid":762143,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"屎上最貴豆腐渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"原來啲中国大豆拎哂去起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123a75461fd57788570d2e638eb65abbf39c0e47","tid":762143,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb3ef748879218d9d499541b43a66ed667639ede","tid":762143,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite